Create a Lead Generation Messenger Chatbot using Chatfuel is a course organized by Course Project Network that aims to create an automated client conversation tool using an automated conversational robot called Chatfuel. This course also teaches how to manage consumer contact data so there is no need to make contacts or conversations manually. This course is great because it can help an entrepreneur in keeping his customers informed quickly and concisely.

This course is a project created by the Coursera project network, which takes about 2 hours to complete. This course can be done through rhythm on the Coursera or directly on the browser you are using. In this course, there are six tasks that must be done, namely creating a chatfuel account, creating a welcome message and menu section, making a book a test drive section, creating an explore new offer section, creating a talk to an advisor section, and connect with Google Sheets and test the bots that have been created. In addition to these tasks, there is also a quiz with six questions. This course can also be applied in different models, for example, in selling bread, clothes, or other goods. In this course, the platform used for the chatbot is Facebook, but Chatfuel also offers chatbots for Instagram and websites. This course helped me in creating a chatbot for a Facebook page. However, there are a few problems working on this chatbot because this chatbot can only be used on the Facebook page. It cannot be used for personal Facebook accounts. On the other hand, the submission of material by the teacher is quite easy to understand, even with the help of subtitles on the video tutorial. This course can be said to be very interesting for me to learn because making chatbots using chatfuel is a new thing that I have learned.
